<%= render 'components/navbar' %>
<div class="banner-lp-img">
    <div class="banner about" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4),rgba(0,0,0,0.4)), url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1621112904887-419379ce6824?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1772&q=80);">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="banner-lp about">
          <h1>Choose. Propose. Experience.</h1>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-about">
    <div class="container-lp about">
      <div class="flex-about-first-block first">
        <div class="img-about">
          <%= image_tag "block2.jpg", height: 350, width: 550, crop: :fill, class: "article-img" %>
        </div>
        <div class="about-main-key">
          <h4>The Platform <br>Connecting <br>Employees <br>Worldwide</h4>
          <p><i class="fa-solid fa-globe"></i> 20 Partner Companies</p>
          <p><i class="fa-solid fa-key"></i> +300 exchanges</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex-about-first-block second">
        <div class="img-about">
          <%= image_tag "pool.jpg", height: 350, width: 550, crop: :fill, class: "article-img" %>
        </div>
        <div class="about-main-key">
          <h4>Exchange Homes,<br>Discover the World</h4>
          <p>Sucasa connects you with a vibrant community of fellow employees who are eager to share their homes and embark on their own adventures. <br>By exchanging homes with colleagues from different departments, locations, or even countries, you can <b>swap your everyday surroundings</b> for exciting new environments, adding a unique twist to your travel experiences.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex-about-first-block first">
        <div class="img-about">
          <%= image_tag "block5.jpg", height: 350, width: 550, crop: :fill, class: "article-img" %>
        </div>
        <div class="about-main-key">
      <h4>Experience the<br>Joy of Free Travel</h4>
          <p>Imagine being able to explore your dream destinations without worrying about the hefty price tag. <br>With SuCasa, you can turn your travel dreams into reality, enjoying the freedom to visit new places, immerse yourself in different cultures, and create lifelong memories, all <b>without spending a dime</b> on accommodation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex-about-first-block second">
        <div class="img-about">
          <%= image_tag "travel.jpg", height: 350, width: 550, crop: :fill, class: "article-img" %>
        </div>
        <div class="about-main-key">
          <h4>Embrace Sustainable<br>Practices</h4>
          <p>By optimizing the use of existing resources and minimizing the carbon footprint associated with business travel, you contribute to a <b>greener future.</b></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex-about-first-block first">
        <div class="img-about">
          <%= image_tag "block3.jpg", height: 350, width: 550, crop: :fill, class: "article-img" %>
        </div>
        <div class="about-main-key">
        <h4>Foster Meaningful<br>Connections</h4>
          <p>Through SuCasa, you'll not only gain access to free travel but also have the chance to <b>forge meaningful connections</b> with colleagues who share your love for adventure. <br>Exchange tips, swap travel stories, and build lasting friendships with like-minded explorers from various departments and locations, fostering a sense of unity and camaraderie within our organization.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="banner about2" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4),rgba(0,0,0,0.4)), url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1621112904887-419379ce6824?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1772&q=80);">
    <div class="btn-article">
      <%= link_to "Exchange my home", "/about", class: "btn-article" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<%= render 'components/footer' %>
